(608, 'manual', 'xenforo112', '[ul] 	[li]The first thing you need is to install the addon ''Kotomi'', if you have not installed it yet.[/li] 	[li]Therefor, download the file ''addon-Kotomi.zip'' from step 1. Unpack it, and upload the contained folder ''library'' to your XenForo installation.[/li] 	[li]Then download the file ''addon-Kotomi.xml'' from step 1. Save it on your desktop for example.[/li] 	[li]Open the adminpanel of XenForo, goto ''Home'' -> ''Addons'' -> ''Install Addon''.[/li] 	[li]At ''Install from uploaded file:'', select the file ''addon-Kotomi.xml'' from your desktop. Click onto ''Install Addon''.[/li] 	[li]Now download the file ''ezstats2_bf3.php'' from step 1. Upload it to the root folder of your XenForo installation.[/li] 	[li]The URL to your Leaderboard is now ''http://www.yoursite.com/ezstats2_bf3.php''.[/li] 	[li]If you want to make the leaderboard accessible in the board structure, then open the adminpanel of XenForo, goto ''Applications'' -> ''Create New Link Forum''.[/li] 	[li]Enter a title, select a parent node and as ''Link URL'' enter ''ezstats2_bf3.php''. At last click onto ''Save Link Forum''. The leaderboard is linked now in your forum.[/li] [/ul]', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', ''),
